@startuml seq_attendance_checkin
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: Attendance Check-in / Check-out Flow

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Staff" as Staff
participant "React SPA" as Client
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Attendance Service" as Attendance
participant "Prom-client" as Metrics
database "PostgreSQL (HA)" as PG

Staff -> Client : Click "Check-in" button
Client -> Client : Get Local Time & Calculate Late Minutes
Client -> Gateway : POST /api/attendance/verify-code \n(device_id, late_minutes, type)
Gateway -> Attendance : Route Request

Attendance -> Metrics : Intercept Request (Start Timer)
Attendance -> Attendance : Verify JWT & Extract user_id

Note over Attendance, PG: Idempotent DB Operation
Attendance -> PG : INSERT INTO attendance_logs \nON CONFLICT (user_id, work_date) \nDO UPDATE SET check_in_time = EXCLUDED...
PG --> Attendance : Acknowledge Upsert

Attendance -> Attendance : Log action (Grafana Loki format)
Attendance -> Metrics : Res.on('finish') -> Record Duration & Increment Counter

Attendance -> Client : 200 OK (Success Message)
Client -> Staff : Update UI (Status: "Đang Làm")

@enduml